{"tid":1150695,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王全璋家書稱後悔 妻驚訝：如進黨校四年","createTime":"2019-05-12T05:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T07:10:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b79922f13c79f714df524577619dc9e68a7959","tid":1150695,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:05:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190512/20676427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F20676427&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW%2Fuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=be8f9cb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F20676427&h=9e47030a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190512/20676427</a><br />\n<br />\n王全璋家書稱後悔 妻驚訝：如進黨校四年<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190512/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190512%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=ef97ad48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李文足（右）公開王全璋（左）在獄中寄來的首封家書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地「709系列案」維權律師王全璋被失蹤到秘密判監、送監服刑，至今近4年一直未能與家人見面。近日其給妻子李文足的首封家書曝光，李稱信中文字確為丈夫手迹，惟內容令她不敢相信。信中不但讚監獄「環境良好」，又謂羈押期間「一直反思自己所犯錯誤」，感內疚並向家人致歉。李大表驚訝稱丈夫「越來越陌生」，質疑他儼如「去黨校進修了4年」！<br />\n<br />\n王全璋2015年7月被拘，後被當局以涉嫌顛覆罪逮捕，去年12月24日在天津市中級法院閉門審理，今年1月底被判囚4年6個月，上月底移送至山東臨沂監獄服刑。過去4年，李文足一直以各種方式為丈夫維權，但一直未能相見。前天她公開丈夫從監獄寄出的三頁家書，首度披露上訴已於4月28日被天津市高級法院駁回。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「監獄環境真舒適」<br />\n<br />\n最令李文足難以置信的是，丈夫在信中表現悔改之意，又誇「監獄環境真舒適」，稱「我現在有相對自由的空間，能在院子散步、活動，飲食也有很大的改善」；又稱在羈押期間「一直反思自己所犯錯誤，由於我的誤判，我對歷史和政治的無知，失去一系列機會，給親人帶來巨大的困擾和傷痛，我深感內疚」，要家人「原諒我這一生放縱不羈」。李文足網上寫道：「猛看很熟悉的字體，越來越陌生了。」「你好像不是被失蹤、被酷刑、與外界隔絕了4年，倒像是去黨校進修了4年！」「我也不聽你指揮了！我必須去見你，而且要見到你！」<br />\n<br />\nTwitter  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n科網公司常加班 員工猝死<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n內地通緝犯花近千萬送女入耶魯"},{"pid":"04d1b28117d47e5a4694ed09128c1bb838b0915a","tid":1150695,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"桂民海都拍片認錯喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e9ebf002def4b640b199b2fc50a0e25d509bfd","tid":1150695,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"送中條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea19155efe1c9e41a357646009ce39a5c4234aaa","tid":1150695,"uid":24730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"「原諒我這一生放縱不羈」呢句暗示佢「愛自由」"},{"pid":"6a682ae174aab5705906405b7d6d9a7ee706532d","tid":1150695,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea19155efe1c9e41a357646009ce39a5c4234aaa","tid":1150695,"uid":24730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"「原諒我這一生放縱不羈」呢句暗示佢「愛自由」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7553d652e3d517e92405134ef1b34a894a5f223f","tid":1150695,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea191